---
import SectionTitle from "../../ui/SectionTitle.astro";
import Container from "../../ui/Container.astro";
---

<section id="our-story" class="bg-white py-16 md:py-24">
  <Container class="!max-w-[1200px]">
    <div class="grid gap-12 lg:grid-cols-[1.02fr_0.98fr] lg:items-start">
      <div class="space-y-8">
        <SectionTitle
          eyebrow="WE ARE ANAN PACK"
          title="ANAN PACK is a packaging and trim supply chain partner for apparel, home textile, lifestyle, and e-commerce brands."
          description="We focus on helping growing brands manage sourcing with more clarity and less friction. From hang tags and labels to packaging boxes, ribbons, and retail-ready kits, we bridge design intent with reliable manufacturing execution."
          align="left"
        />
        <div class="grid gap-6 sm:grid-cols-2">
          <div class="overflow-hidden rounded-soft shadow-card">
            <img
              src="/images/about/about-story-flatlay.png"
              alt="Custom hang tags, labels, and trim materials laid out on a work surface"
              class="aspect-[1.15/1] size-full object-cover"
              loading="lazy"
              decoding="async"
            />
          </div>
          <div class="overflow-hidden rounded-soft shadow-card sm:translate-y-10">
            <img
              src="/images/about/about-story-packing.png"
              alt="A packaging shipment being checked and handed over"
              class="aspect-[1.15/1] size-full object-cover"
              loading="lazy"
              decoding="async"
            />
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="rounded-card bg-surface-muted p-7 md:p-9">
        <SectionTitle
          eyebrow="WHY WE STARTED"
          title="We created this team to solve the real challenges of sourcing in China."
          align="left"
        />
        <div class="mt-6 space-y-4 text-sm leading-7 text-text-muted md:text-[15px]">
          <p>
            Many overseas brands need more than a single supplier. They need a sourcing partner who can coordinate multiple categories, review artwork, check production progress, and keep communication consistent.
          </p>
          <p>
            Instead of sending clients from one factory to another, we built a practical system around supplier verification, project management, quality follow-up, and delivery planning.
          </p>
          <p>
            The result is a workflow that helps brands move faster, reduce avoidable mistakes, and scale packaging programs with more confidence.
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </Container>
</section>
